text: Haris Tuharea (born in November 22, 1994) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a left winger for Liga 1 club Madura United. ==Career== ===PS Mojokerto Putra=== In 2017, Tuharea signed a year contract with PS Mojokerto Putra. Tuharea scored 10 goals in the 2018 season, when PSMP played in the second division. ===PSS Sleman=== On 28 January 2019, Tuharea signed a year contract with PSS Sleman along other players, Derry Rachman, Ricky Kambuaya, and Jajang Sukmara. ==References== == External links == * Haris Tuharea at Soccerway * Haris Tuharea at Liga Indonesia Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:PSS Sleman players Category:PS Mojokerto Putra players
